---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import profilePic from "../assets/yo.jpeg";
---

<Layout>
	<section
		id="about"
		class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center max-w-5xl rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16 gap-8 md:gap-12 mx-auto about-card"
	>
		<div class="flex-shrink-0">
			<Image
				src={profilePic}
				alt="Foto de perfil de Marcelo Aguirre"
				width="280"
				height="280"
				fetchpriority="high"
				class="rounded-full border-4 shadow-2xl mb-6 lg:mb-0 object-cover w-64 h-64 md:w-72 md:h-72"
			/>
		</div>
		<div class="text-center lg:text-left flex-1 space-y-6">
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<!-- Contenido en Español -->
				<div x-show="language === 'es'">
					<p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
						<strong class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">¡Hola!</strong> Soy un desarrollador web full-stack de Uruguay
						con experiencia en proyectos por toda Latinoamérica. Trabajo con
						tecnologías modernas como <strong class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">NestJS</strong>, <strong class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">NextJS</strong>,
						<strong class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">Astro</strong>, <strong class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">Supabase</strong>, <strong class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-300">PostgreSQL</strong>,
						<strong class="text-green-500 dark:text-green-300">MongoDB</strong>, <strong class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-300">Docker</strong> y <strong class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400">n8n</strong> para automatización. Mi experiencia con <strong class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">servidores Linux</strong> me permite implementar despliegues eficientes en entornos de producción.
					</p>
					<p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
						Mi pasión por emprender e innovar me impulsa a buscar
						constantemente soluciones y estar al tanto de las últimas
						tecnologías. Soy autodidacta, por eso siempre estoy aprendiendo
						y adaptándome a los avances del campo.
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<!-- Contenido en Inglés -->
				<div x-show="language === 'en'">
					<p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
						<strong class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Hello!</</strong> I'm a full-stack web developer from Uruguay
						with experience in projects throughout Latin America. I work with
						modern technologies like <strong class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400">NestJS</strong>, <strong class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">NextJS</strong>,
						<strong class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">Astro</strong>, <strong class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">Supabase</strong>, <strong class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-300">PostgreSQL</strong>,
						<strong class="text-green-500 dark:text-green-300">MongoDB</strong>, <strong class="text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-300">Docker</strong> and <strong class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400">n8n</strong> for automation. My experience with <strong class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400">Linux servers</strong> allows me to implement efficient deployments in production environments.
					</p>
					<p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
						My passion for entrepreneurship and innovation drives me to constantly
						seek solutions and stay up to date with the latest technologies.
						I'm self-taught, which is why I'm always learning and adapting
						to advances in the field.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
